# CoinBull.app Security Policy

CoinBull.app is a secure application for creating and managing Solana tokens. We take security seriously and implement best practices for wallet connections.

## Wallet Connections

We use secure methods to connect to wallets including Phantom, Solflare, and other Solana wallets. We only request the minimum necessary permissions for token creation and management.

## Data Security

We do not store private keys or seed phrases. All interactions with wallets happen through secure, approved RPC connections following Solana's security standards.

## Reporting Security Issues

If you discover any security issues, please report them to security@coinbull.app.

## Phantom Wallet Integration

This application has been audited for secure integration with Phantom wallet and follows all recommended security practices. 